channel.title: I need help with removing doors! [PI]
channel.description:
kk, if anyone could help with this ...
Always when i add this code in doors.cfg
[code]door = 2510 3680 0 0 1 [/code]
Then, I compile and I click runserver.bat (wich puts server on)
Then it says
[code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ExceptionInInitializerError Caused by: java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "2510 3680 0 0 1" at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(NumberFormatException. java:65) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:492) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:527) at server.world.ObjectHandler.loadDoorConfig(ObjectHandler.java:284) at server.world.ObjectHandler.<init>(ObjectHandler.java:26) at server.Server.<clinit>(Server.java:64) Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Yeah i know, there is some kind of topics about it, but I didn't find any good solution :) So ty so much if you would help me with this small problem.
